*[http://wiki.openwrt.org/toh/gigaset/sx76x ''Siemens Gigaset SX762'' on '''OpenWrt''' wiki]
Per the OpenWrt wiki, v2 devices have part numbers following the S30852-S70x-xxxx pattern :S30852-S709-R331-5 and S30852-S706-R331-5 may be valid Siemens part numbers. Only firmware version 4.x.x.x.x devices are described here (that is, v2 devices).
*[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=148426 On the DD-WRT forums]
Same model is manufactured in Germany by both [[Siemens]] and [[Sagem]], :and in Tunisia only by [[Sagem]]. Known MAC OUIs: 00:21:04, 00:26:91, 98:8B:5D, C0:D0:44
